ented technologies, <span class=\"cangc3\">C</span><span class=\"cangc4\">LEAN</span> <span class=\"cangc3\">A</span><span class=\"cangc4\">S</span> <span class=\"cangc3\">N</span><span class=\"cangc4\">EW</span><sup>&reg;</sup> provides offsite cleaning for heat exchangers and other process components, bringing them to &ldquo;like-new&rdquo; performance and efficiency levels.</p>\r\n<p>We welcome the opportunity to demonstrate the value of a cleaner, faster, safer, and greener solution. Come in and see for yourself at 1303 Thompson Park Dr., Baytown, TX 77521.</p>', 'mx', '2020-12-26 19:23:51', '2020-12-26 19:23:51');
