m; color: #227cbe;\">A</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.9em; color: #227cbe;\">S</span>&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size: 1.15em; color: #227cbe;\">N</span><span style=\"font-size: 0.9em; color: #227cbe;\">EW</span><sup style=\"font-size: 1.1em; color: #227cbe;\">&reg;</sup>&nbsp;will:</p>\n            <ul style=\"list-style-type: none;\">\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Checkmark!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" />&nbsp;Work with you to determine the right size basket for your needs.</li>\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Checkmark!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" />&nbsp;Drop a basket on your wash pad and you can fill it with your parts.</li>\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Checkmark!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\"  />&nbsp;Pick up that basket when it&rsquo;s full or you need the cleaning done.</li>\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Checkmark!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" />&nbsp;Clean your parts for a guaranteed, fixed price.</li>\n            <li><img style=\"height: auto;\" src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" alt=\"Checkmark!\" data-src=\"https://cleanasnew.com/assets/img/service-green-checkmark2.png\" />&nbsp;Return your basket of clean parts the next day!</li>\n            </ul>\n            <p>Check out our&nbsp;<a href=\"http://localhost:3000/posts/basket-of-parts\" aria-invalid=\"true\">&ldquo;By The Basket&rdquo; services video</a>&nbsp;and give us a call today to arrange a &ldquo;By The