apabilities and strategic management to meet your needs.', 'Our Services - Offsite Cleaning, By The Basket, Wash Pad...', ' ', 'CLEANER, FASTER, SAFER & GREENER - Clean As New® | Baytown TX', 'We deliver a new standard in cleaning performance with results that are CLEANER, FASTER, SAFER AND GREENER than traditional hydroblasting.  This means energy savings, quicker completion times, better results and more.', 'Energy Saved, Shorter Shutdowns, Reduced Environmental Impact', 'I thought everything you guys did was awesome and have already been spreading recommendations to continue using you guys whenever we can! - Shell Deer Park', 'Heat Exchanger Cleaning: Your Questions Answered - Clean As New®', 'Do you have a question on heat exchanger cleaning? Ask the experts from the Clean As New® offsite facility. Click here to read our recent FAQs.', 'Heat Exchanger Cleaning - Testimonials - Clean As New®', 'We welcome the opportunity to demonstrate the value of a  CLEANER, FASTER, SAFER AND GREENER solution. Come in and see for yourself at 1303 Thompson Park Drive, Baytown, Texas 77521 USA.', 'About Us - Clean As New®', 'Clean As New® is a subsidiary joint venture of Tech Sonic LP. Tech Sonic got its start in the oil sands region of Canada as a hydroblasting company nearly 20 years ago and began experimenting with ultrasonics in the early 2000’s.', 'Clean As New ® at 1.832.271.2666', 'Questions regarding our industrial cleaning services? Contact Clean As New® at info@cleanasnew.com or visit us at 1303 Thompson Park Drive, Baytown, Texas 77521 USA.', ' <h1>Oops! We lost that page.</h1>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class=\"quotation\">We\'re very sorry, but the page you requested cannot be found. It may have been moved or deleted. <br />For more information, please visit our site and check out great content such as <a href=\"../testimonials/case-studies\">Tech Sonic Case Studies</a>, <a href=\"faq\">Heat Exchanger FAQs</a> and <a href=\"../testimonials/referred-journal-publications\">