ean As New® (China)', 'Clean As New® delivers industrial cleaning services both onsite and offsite. We ensure 100% clean. If we can’t clean it, you don’t pay!', 'How We Compare [Cleaning Cost, Heat Exchanger Performance]', 'Our combination of Tech Sonic ultrasonic technology and hydroblasting cleans compact exchanger designs on the shell side, where hydroblasting alone fails.', 'Heat Exchangers Cleaning [Straight Tube, Twisted Tube] - Clean As New®', 'If you require a quick turnaround solution, Clean As New® has the know-how, capabilities and strategic management to meet your needs.', 'Our Services - Offsite Cleaning, By The Basket, Wash Pad...', ' ', 'CLEANER, FASTER, SAFER & GREENER - Clean As New® | Baytown TX', 'We deliver a new standard in cleaning performance with results that are CLEANER, FASTER, SAFER AND GREENER than traditional hydroblasting.  This means energy savings, quicker completion times, better results and more.', 'Energy Saved, Shorter Shutdowns, Reduced Environmental Impact', 'I thought everything you guys did was awesome and have already been spreading recommendations to continue using you guys whenever we can! - Shell Deer Park', 'Heat Exchanger Cleaning: Your Questions Answered - Clean As New®', 'Do you have a question on heat exchanger cleaning? Ask the experts from the Clean As New® offsite facility. Click here to read our recent FAQs.', 'Heat Exchanger Cleaning - Testimonials - Clean As New®', 'We welcome the opportunity to demonstrate the value of a  CLEANER, FASTER, SAFER AND GREENER solution. Come in and see for yourself at 1303 Thompson Park Drive, Baytown, Texas 77521 USA.', 'About Us - Clean As New®', 'Clean As New® is a subsidiary joint venture of Tech Sonic LP. Tech Sonic got its start in the oil sands region of Canada as a hydroblasting company nearly 20 years ago and began experimenting with ultrasonics in the early 2000’s.', 'Clean As New ® at 1.832.271.2666', 'Questions regarding our industrial cleaning services? Contact Clean As New® at info@cleanasnew.com or visit us at 1303 Thompson Park Drive, Baytown, Texas 77521 USA.', ' <h1>Oops! We lost that page.</h1>\r\n<blockquote>\r\n<p class=\"quotation\">We\'re very sorry, but the page you requested cannot be found. It may have been moved or deleted. <br />For more information, please visit our site and check out great content such as <a href=\"../testimonials/case-studies\">Tech Sonic Case Studies</a>, <a href=\"faq\">Heat Exchanger FAQs</a> and <a href=\"../testimonials/referred-journal-publications\">Journal Publications</a>.</p>\r\n-<span class=\"cangc\">C</span><span class=\"cangc2\">LEAN</span> <span class=\"cangc\">A</span><span class=\"cangc2\">S</span> <span class=\"cangc\">N</span><span class=\"cangc2\">EW</span><sup>&reg;</sup></blockquote>', '  <h1>410 Gone</h1>\r\n<p>We\'re very sorry, but the page you requested was permanently deleted.</p>', '  <h1>Page Not Found</h1>\r\n<p>If you have reached this page, the content you are seeking has been moved or is no longer available. We are providing links below to more popular pages. If you are still unable to find your information, please contact us.</p>', '<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>\r\n<p>This Privacy Policy (&ldquo;Privacy Policy&rdquo;) governs the manner in which Clean As New Gulf Coast, LLC (&ldquo;CANGC&rdquo;, &ldquo;us&rdquo;, &ldquo;our&rdquo;, and &ldquo;we&rdquo;) collects, uses, maintains and discloses information collected from users (each, a \"User\", &ldquo;you&rdquo; or &ldquo;your&rdquo;) of the <a href=\"https://cleanasnew.com/\">www.cleanasnew.com</a> website (\"Site\" or &ldquo;Website&rdquo;). This Privacy Policy applies to the Site and all products and services offered by CANGC. Our Privacy Policy is designed to help you understand how we collect, use and safeguard the information you provide to us and to assist you in making informed decisions when using our services.</p>\r\n<p>By using this Site, you signify your acceptance of this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree